           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6489-5443"))
Description: Generate tibble with departure times using user-defined: sampling method, date, time-window, path and file name. Supports four sampling methods (Systematic, Simple Random, Hybrid and Constrained Random Walk Sampling). 
